            <title>[FELIX-3971] [DS] SingleDynamicCustomizer doesn&apos;t respond correctly to configuration update events.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3971</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SingleDynamicCustomizer.addedService only processes events if they were not in the previous satisfied set for the old config.  But the config may have changed which service satisfies the filter.  We need different logic here.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;            if ( getPreviousRefMap().remove( serviceReference ) == null )&lt;br/&gt;
works for multipleDynamicCustomizer, but not the single one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
